jarvis 1.0.1-SNAPSHOT API

Core 
Package Description
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.core
Contains the core components of the Jarvis framework.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.core.platform
Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom platforms.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.core.platform.action
Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom platform's actions.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.core.platform.io
Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom platform's input provider.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.core.recognition
Contains the abstract classes to implement to provide custom intent recognition.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.core.recognition.dialogflow
An intent recognition implementation for the DialogFlow platform.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.core.server
Contains the Jarvis server implementation.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.core.session
Contains the classes to manage sessions and contexts.
Plugins 
Package Description
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.plugins
Contains the Jarvis plugins bundled with the standard Jarvis distribution.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.plugins.core
The root package of the Jarvis Core plugin.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.plugins.core.platform
Contains the platform implementation of the Jarvis Core plugin.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.plugins.core.platform.action
Contains the action implementations available in the Jarvis Core platform.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.plugins.discord
The root package of the Jarvis Discord plugin.

edu.uoc.som.jarvis.plugins.discord.platform.io

Models 
Package Description
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.execution
Contains the interfaces to manipulate Execution models.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.execution.impl
Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Execution models.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.execution.util
Contains utility classes used to manipulate Execution models.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.intent
Contains the interfaces to manipulate Intent models.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.intent.impl
Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Intent models.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.intent.util
Contains utility classes used to manipulate Intent models.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.platform
Contains the interfaces to manipulate Platform models.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.platform.impl
Contains the implementation classes used to manipulate Platform models.
edu.uoc.som.jarvis.platform.util
Contains utility classes used to manipulate Platform models.
